<%# 2026-05-19 (Bug A3 fix) — sync row now carries a stable id +
    modifier class + `data-resyncing` yes/no attribute so Turbo's
    morph refresh (page-level `auto-refresh` controller polling every
    5s while `resyncing?` is true) reliably swaps the value cell text
    from `~Xm ago` → `---` and back. Date / dev / pub rows render
    unchanged.

    2026-05-19 (Wave B) — during resync, the date / dev / pub rows
    render their value cells as `sync-indicator` dot-loaders at phase
    offsets 1 / 2 / 3 (genre line is offset 0, summary is back to 0).
    The static `title` attribute on those cells points at the loader
    seed frame so screen-reader hover is consistent with the visible
    text on connect. The sync row itself keeps its existing static
    `---` value text (semantic meaning is "when did sync last land"
    — the row-level `--syncing` dim layer carries the muted-stale
    treatment without an in-cell loader). %>
<table class="kv-table" style="margin: 6px 0 0 0;">
  <tbody>
    <% meta_rows.each do |row| %>
      <% if row[:key] == Game::MetaTableComponent::SYNC_ROW_KEY %>
        <tr id="<%= sync_row_id %>"
            class="<%= 'kv-table__row--syncing' if resyncing? %>"
            data-resyncing="<%= resyncing? ? 'yes' : 'no' %>">
          <td class="kv-table__label"><%= row[:label] %></td>
          <td class="kv-table__value" title="<%= row[:value] %>"><%= row[:value] %></td>
        </tr>
      <% else %>
        <tr>
          <td class="kv-table__label"><%= row[:label] %></td>
          <% if resyncing? %>
            <% offset = phase_offset_for(row[:key]) %>
            <% seed = Game::MetaTableComponent::SYNC_INDICATOR_FRAMES[offset] %>
            <td class="kv-table__value kv-table__value--syncing"
                title="<%= seed %>"
                data-controller="sync-indicator"
                data-sync-indicator-frames-value="<%= Game::MetaTableComponent::SYNC_INDICATOR_FRAMES.to_json %>"
                data-sync-indicator-phase-offset-value="<%= offset %>"
                data-resyncing="yes"
                aria-live="polite"><%= seed %></td>
          <% else %>
            <td class="kv-table__value" title="<%= row[:value] %>"><%= row[:value] %></td>
          <% end %>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
